text: Where did Obi-Wan take Luke after his birth? Tatooine.
Who is Palpatine’s granddaughter? Rey.
Who are Kylo Ren’s parents? Han Solo and Princess Leia.
Who was Anakin Skywalker’s Padawan? Ahsoka Tano.
Who had the highest midi-chlorian count in Star Wars? Anakin Skywalker.
Who built C-3PO? Anakin Skywalker.
Who had Rey’s parents taken and killed? Palpatine.
Anakin Skywalker grew up to be who? Darth Vader.
Who is Luke and Leia’s father? Darth Vader.
Who is Darth Vader’s grandson? Kylo Ren.
Who killed Snoke? Kylo Ren.
What is the relationship between Rey and Kylo Ren? They are a dyad in the Force.
Who is Luke and Leia’s mother? Padme Amidala.
Who is Chancellor Palpatine’s Sith alter-ego? Darth Sidious.
Who is the First Order’s supreme leader? Snoke.
Who is the famous mentor of Luke Skywalker? Obi-wan Kenobi.
Which weapon is used by the Jedi Knights? Lightsaber.
Who is the twin brother of Princess Leia? Luke Skywalker.
Who is the Queen of the planet Naboo? Padme Amidala.
Who is the oldest living Jedi, who is also the oldest on the Council? Yoda.
